'''''Silver Leaves''''' is a journal for fans of [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] and fantasy literature. It was formerly the official journal of [[The White Tree Fund]], but is now published by [[Oloris Publishing]].<ref name="1.1">{{webcite|author= lilymilos|articleurl=http://news.mymiddleearth.com/2013/02/07/oloris-publishing-acquires-silver-leaves-journal/|articlename=Oloris Publishing Acquires Silver Leaves Journal|dated=7-Feb-2013|website=MEN|accessed=9-Feb-2013}}</ref>
